name: Synthcity Streets - EP 3: Exploding Expectations - Standard Edition
description:
Play the third episode of Synthcity Streets and try your hand at taking back the streets of Synthcity!                  
Controls - Arrow keys to move, Z,X,C for punch, kick and block. Space to jump, ESC, Enter and left click to navigate menus and cutscenes                   
Please use a desktop browser - Works with Chrome, MS Edge,  Brave doesn’t seem to like WebGLs however. Play in full screen for the best experience  
Thank you for playing Synthcity Streets, please consider purchasing the game to help fund future episodes | @Discowarlock on twitter, dm any questions or bugs
